🏋️‍♂️ Fit-Tech

A modern Fitness & Sports Website designed to promote health, exercise, and sports awareness. Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, this project showcases fitness-related content, images, and interactivity.

🚀 Features

🖼️ Attractive fitness-themed UI

📱 Responsive design (works on mobile, tablet, and desktop)

⚡ Lightweight and fast

🎨 Custom styling with style.css

🧑‍💻 Interactive elements using script.js

🛠️ Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

Assets: Fitness images (.jpg) stored in /static/images

Fit-Tech/
│── static/
│   ├── images/           # All fitness-related images
│   │   ├── about-background.jpg
│   │   ├── background.jpg
│   │   ├── input-pic.jpg
│   │   ├── plankingMan.jpg
│   │   ├── runningGirl.jpg
│   │   ├── some.jpg
│   │   ├── sportspic.jpg
│── template/             # (Optional templates if added later)
│── index.html            # Main landing page
│── style.css             # Stylesheet
│── script.js             # JavaScript logic
│── readme.md             # Project documentation
⚡ Getting Started

Clone this repository
git clone https://github.com/itsReek/Fit--tech.git
cd Fit--tech
Open in Browser
Just open index.html in your browser.

(Optional) Use Live Server Extension in VS Code for auto-refresh while editing.

🎯 Future Enhancements

Add a BMI Calculator

